name: Moon-Eclipsing Dragon God
outcome: {AttackerName} ascends even higher, her arms spread wide, almost eclipsing the gigantic moon behind her! Her long hair flows gracefully in the wind, as she casts a single solemn glance in your direction before closing her eyes... It looks very majestic, but you're not sure if it actually does anything!
